---
title: Apricot Chicken Tikka & Spinach Rice with Tomato Salsa & Cashews
description: Tick this off your want-to-eat list tonight because this chicken tikka will blow you away. We’ve even added an apricot sauce to
glaze the chicken for that fruit hit we all love. The lush green of the spinach rice will soak up all the glaze and leave you feeling
very satisfied.
